'''Rion''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] living during the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], and was part of the [[Corellian Resistance/Legends|Corellian underground rebel group]] that opposed the rule of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

While Rebel spy [[Bria Tharen]] embedded herself at the Imperial headquarters on Corellia, Rion served as her go-between, relaying the intelligence she had gathered to the leaders of the Corellian Resistance.

